---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Rituals in Plain Sight — Sun Worship — Nazaryah"
  description="Every year billions of people perform rituals rooted in sun worship without knowing it. Easter, Christmas, Yule — none of it came from Scripture."
>
  <div class="sw-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="sw-hero">
      <p class="sw-label">&#8213; Sun Worship &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="sw-title">Rituals in Plain Sight</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        The holidays billions observe every year — and where they actually came from.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INTRO ── -->
    <section class="sw-section">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p>
          Every year, billions of people perform rituals rooted in sun worship without knowing it — Easter sunrise services, Christmas trees, Yule logs, hot cross buns stamped with the cross of Tammuz, and celebrations timed to solstices the Torah never commanded.
        </p>
        <p>
          This page breaks down the major holidays one by one, showing what you are actually participating in, where the traditions really came from, and what Yahuah actually commanded His people to observe instead.
        </p>
        <p>
          The question is not whether these days feel meaningful. The question is: <em>who told you to observe them?</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── COMING SOON ── -->
    <section class="sw-section sw-section-alt">
      <div class="sw-prose sw-coming-soon">
        <div class="sw-soon-icon">&#9685;</div>
        <h2 class="sw-soon-title">Full Study Coming</h2>
        <p>
          This study is being assembled. Each holiday will be documented individually — its pagan origins, its path into church tradition, and what Scripture actually says about it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Return to the <a href="/sun-worship" class="sw-link">Sun Worship hub</a> or read <a href="/sun-worship/the-ancient-lie" class="sw-link">The Ancient Lie</a> for the full historical thread while this page is being built.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── QUOTE ── -->
    <section class="sw-footer-quote">
      <p class="sw-quote-text">"Thus says Yahuah: Learn not the way of the heathen, and be not dismayed at the signs of heaven; for the heathen are dismayed at them."</p>
      <p class="sw-quote-ref">— Jeremiah 10:2</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sw-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .sw-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.2), transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .sw-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .sw-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sw-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .sw-section-alt {
    background: rgba(10, 6, 2, 0.3);
  }

  .sw-prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
  }

  .sw-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .sw-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sw-prose em { color: #c4a46b; font-style: italic; }

  .sw-link {
    color: #BA7517;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .sw-link:hover { color: #d4930f; }

  .sw-coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sw-soon-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #5a3a10;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sw-soon-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #c4a46b;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .sw-footer-quote {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #160f07 0%, #0e0904 100%);
  }

  .sw-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4a46b;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .sw-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #5a3e1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
